data.description: Newly built in 2022, this Maria Model IS THE LOWEST PRICED MARIA RESALE AND INCLUDES GOLF MEMBERSHIP!! The home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, a heated pool with spa and water/golf views, plank flooring, large island w/ quartz counters, 42" cabinets w/ moldings, tiled backsplash, glass front door, tray ceilings, crown moldings, upgraded lighting, large master suite, cabinets in laundry with built-in sink, screened in pool with upgraded lighting! Amenities will include a 23,000 sqft clubhouse, two restaurants, state of the art fitness center, full-service Spa, resort pool and a lap pool. Plus, 8 tennis and 6 pickleball courts and 2 pro shops. The Ave Maria community has a lot to offer including: parks, walking trails, restaurants, shopping, Publix grocery and so much more!
